{# Claude Code worktree include 规则 — v2.0 多 Agent 并行 (Phase 06 Task 5.3) #}
{# 设计: design/his_bak/v1.1-UNIFIED-DEV-PLAN.md §5.3 + multi-agent §3.5 #}
{# 用途: `claude --worktree` 多 Agent 并行运行时,worktree 只同步下列文件 #}
{#      避免每个 worktree 复制整个项目(~100MB+),节省磁盘 + 加快启动 #}
{# 格式: 每行一条 include 规则,支持 gitignore-style glob (#开头的行为注释) #}
{# 参考: https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/iam/worktrees #}

# === 核心交付物 (必同步) ===
README.md
CLAUDE.md
Makefile
pyproject.toml
package.json
go.mod
Cargo.toml

# === 源码根 ===
src/**
lib/**
app/**
{% if language == 'python' %}auto_engineering/**{% endif %}
{% if language == 'typescript' %}packages/**

# === 配置 ===
config/**
*.yml
*.yaml
*.toml
.env.example

# === 测试 ===
tests/**

# === 文档 ===
docs/**
design/BEACON.md
design/INDEX.md

# === 工作流产物 (worktree 可写) ===
_scratch/**

# === 显式排除 (即使 gitignore 允许也不同步) ===
.git/**
node_modules/**
.venv/**
dist/**
build/**
__pycache__/**
.pytest_cache/**
.coverage